
<div class="container">
	<div class="text-center my-4">
		<h1 class="fw-light">
			<span class="me-2">Welcome to</span>
			<span class="display-4 textAqua ">fleet manager</span>
		</h1>
	</div>
	

	<!-- Sign Up / Sign In Box -->
	<div class="row g-4 justify-content-evenly my-5">
		
		<div class="col-12 col-lg-5">
			<div class="myFrame p-4 h-100 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
				<div>
					<h3 class="text-center">Create Your Account</h3>
					<p>Sign up and manage your own vehicle records securely.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="d-flex flex-column flex-xl-row justify-content-between gap-2 mt-3">
					<div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center ">
						<p>Are you new here?</p>
						<a class="btn btn-gradient btn-200w btn-aqua" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Register">Register</a>
					</div>
					<div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center ">
						<p>Already have an account?</p>
						<a class="btn btn-gradient btn-200w" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="Login">Log in</a>
					</div>									
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
				
		<div class="col-12 col-lg-5">
			<div class="myFrame p-4 h-100 d-flex flex-column justify-content-between">
				<div>
					<h3 class="text-center">Explore Without Registering</h3>
					<p>Try all features instantly using a demo account. No sign-up required.</p>
				</div>
				<form method="post" asp-controller="Account" asp-action="LoginAsDemo" class="mt-3 d-flex justify-content-center">
					<input type="hidden" name="DemoUser" value="true" />
					<button type="submit" class="btn btn-aqua btn-200w">Try Demo</button>
				</form>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	

	<div class="myFrame mb-5 d-flex align-content-center">
		<div class="m-3">
			<h3>Manage Your Vehicles in One Place</h3>
			<p>
				Our application provides a clear and organized way to keep track of all the vehicles in your fleet.
				Users can easily add, edit, or remove individual cars, including key details such as make, model, year,
				and license plate. Each user has access only to their own data – securely and privately.
				You also get insights into the most used and most maintained vehicles in your fleet.
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Manage your vehicle fleet in one place</li>
				<li>Search and sort vehicles by model, brand, or license plate</li>
				<li>Register and log in with secure credentials</li>
				<li>See which vehicle is used most often or requires the most maintenance</li>
				<li>Simple and clean user interface optimized for all devices</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div>
			<img src="/images/home1.png" alt="car-fleet" class="d-none d-xl-block myFrame" />
		</div>
		

	</div>
	<div class="myFrame mb-5 d-flex align-content-center">
		<div class="m-3">
			<h3>Track Every Trip with Ease</h3>
			<p>
				Keep detailed logs of every trip taken with your vehicles. Record trip dates, purposes, distances, and durations.
				The application also provides trip-based statistics such as average distance per trip, longest journey, and
				the vehicle with the most trips.
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Log trips with date, distance, and purpose</li>				
				<li>View trip history for each vehicle</li>
				<li>Filter and review trip records by date or car</li>
				<li>Monitor total and average kilometers driven</li>
				<li>Find your longest or furthest trip</li>
				<li>See which car is most frequently used for travel</li>
				<li>Track trip duration and frequency over time</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<img src="/images/home2.png" alt="trips" class="d-none d-xl-block myFrame" />
	</div>
	<div class="myFrame mb-5 d-flex align-content-center">
		<div class="m-3">
			<h3>Stay on Top of Vehicle Maintenance</h3>
			<p>
				Log every repair and maintenance task done on your vehicles — from oil changes to major part replacements.
				Each repair record is tied to a specific vehicle and includes dates, mileage, and descriptions to help you monitor 
				technical condition over time.The app summarizes repair costs, highlights the most expensive cars to maintain, and tracks downtime due to repairs.				
			</p>
			<ul>
				<li>Log repairs with cost, service time, and description</li>
				<li>View total and average repair costs per vehicle</li>
				<li>Identify cars with longest service times</li>
				<li>Find out which vehicle is the most costly to maintain</li>
				<li>Filter repairs by vehicle or date</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<img src="/images/home3.png" alt="repairs" class="d-none d-xl-block myFrame" />
	</div>
</div>

